WEBVTT

00:00.266 --> 00:00.817
Excuse me!

00:01.876 --> 00:02.565
Can I help you?

00:02.933 --> 00:04.376
Yes. Where is the post office?

00:04.741 --> 00:05.619
The post office?

00:06.112 --> 00:08.311
It's over there, next to the cafe.

00:08.691 --> 00:11.127
Ah, yes. I can see it. Thanks

00:11.693 --> 00:13.981
Sorry. I'm on holiday here and I don't know my way around.

00:14.147 --> 00:14.748
No problem.

00:15.123 --> 00:15.405
Bye.

00:15.567 --> 00:15.944
Goodbye!

00:16.247 --> 00:17.150
And have a nice holiday.

00:17.445 --> 00:18.041
Thanks a lot.

